highlights.text: “Hype Man” by DON BROCO is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs United Kingdom, up 12 spots at #50.
“Nice To Each Other” by Olivia Dean has been on Viral Songs United Kingdom the longest, at 94 days straight.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Viral Songs United Kingdom. “Tears” is the highest at #14.
“I Just Wanna” by Lezzs is the highest new entry on Viral Songs United Kingdom at #3.
